name: Console OS - Native Android Remastered for the PC
caption: consoleos.com
description: Introducing Console OS with Android™ Inside. We’ve taken Android apart, and put it back together for your PC. Console OS is a fork of Android designed to take everything that has made mobile awesome, and bring it back to your PC.
